707455f-a.text:
Wyckoff Ave., south side, west from Madison Street to Myrtle Ave. (elevated structure thereon), showing a group of buildings belonging to Welz and Zerweck, brewers. These buildings were razed in 1926.
June 1925.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
